♪A cool breeze drifts away.♪

00:43:34.940 --> 00:43:37.540
♪The rain leaves with the wind
and never returns.♪

00:43:38.220 --> 00:43:43.300
♪Whose dream am I in?♪

00:43:44.260 --> 00:43:47.300
♪Feel the changes in life.♪

00:43:48.220 --> 00:43:50.620
♪I thought a smile could conceal the crease
between my brows.♪

00:43:50.620 --> 00:43:53.620
♪No time has been lost.♪

00:43:53.900 --> 00:43:56.780
♪Things would develop against wishes.♪

00:43:58.020 --> 00:44:00.540
♪It's hard to keep up with time.♪

00:44:01.380 --> 00:44:04.020
♪I'll follow you to the farthest corner.♪

00:44:04.580 --> 00:44:09.660
♪I can't read your mind.
It's all for nothing.♪

00:44:10.740 --> 00:44:13.740
♪Fame is a burden.♪

00:44:14.460 --> 00:44:17.140
♪The longing eventually fades away,♪

00:44:17.180 --> 00:44:20.060
♪leaving people withered♪

00:44:20.380 --> 00:44:23.740
♪and unrepentant.♪

00:44:24.260 --> 00:44:27.580
♪The sounds hitting my ears
are dreamy but real.♪

00:44:27.820 --> 00:44:30.780
♪Rumors spread behind my beck.♪

00:44:31.100 --> 00:44:32.580
♪Spur the horse and gallop.♪

00:44:32.740 --> 00:44:36.740
♪Fail to escape from the design of fate.♪

00:44:37.500 --> 00:44:40.740
♪To what extent can the characters♪

00:44:41.020 --> 00:44:43.020
♪in a story control themselves?♪

00:44:43.460 --> 00:44:44.900
♪Far away from each other,♪

00:44:45.060 --> 00:44:51.460
♪we will end up together.♪

